    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a bare-bones budget ride? Here's an opportunity to snag a vehicle at a seriously low price! We'll be upfront with you \u2014 this car is in poor condition. It does run and drive, but it has noticeable mechanical issues, significant wear and cosmetic damage that will require attention. If you're a handy DIYer or just need something to tinker with, this could be a rewarding find. Priced to reflect its current state, so what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises!",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we believe in complete honesty with every prospective buyer. The exterior shows significant wear throughout \u2014 expect visible rust, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with age and high use. Mechanically, this car requires attention: it runs, but buyers should anticipate the need for repairs and should factor in maintenance costs before purchasing. There may be issues with fluids, belts, filters, or other components that have not been recently serviced. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. No warranties are implied or offered. Please inspect the vehicle in person before purchasing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage a thorough pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 paint retains a deep, uniform gloss with no visible scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. Body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces, moldings, and chrome accents are pristine. The interior is equally impressive, showing virtually no signs of use: upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are unmarked, and every control, switch, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, and the vehicle runs with exceptional smoothness and responsiveness. Service history is complete and up to date. Tires have substantial tread remaining and show even wear. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and presents as close to new as a used car can be. Serious buyers will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Dependable & Ready to Roll! \u2014 Here's a great opportunity to own a genuinely well-maintained vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, has been taken care of over the years, and is ready for daily use without any major concerns. You'll notice normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a comfortable, confident drive. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just need a trustworthy everyday vehicle, this one delivers real value. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
