      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition \u2014 honest and straightforward. The car runs and drives, but it does show its age and use. The exterior has visible wear including scratches, scuffs, and some minor dents that are noticeable on close inspection. The interior shows significant wear on the seats and trim, and there may be some cosmetic issues throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car is functional but may benefit from some attention \u2014 expect that routine maintenance and possibly a few repairs will be needed in the near term. This is a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind putting in a little work or who simply needs reliable transportation without paying a premium for cosmetic perfection. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
